1
00:01:16,610 --> 00:01:17,300
You're awake.

2
00:01:19,090 --> 00:01:20,300
You're quite something, kid.

3
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:22,060
You can even fall asleep in a place like this.

4
00:01:22,610 --> 00:01:23,690
What else am I supposed to do if I don't sleep?

5
00:01:24,010 --> 00:01:24,980
Cut the crap.

6
00:01:25,210 --> 00:01:26,890
Tell me your real identity.

7
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:28,300
And your reason for coming here.

8
00:01:28,690 --> 00:01:30,620
What identity or motive could I possibly have?

9
00:01:30,620 --> 00:01:31,300
I already told you.

10
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:32,460
I'm here to make money.

11
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:33,330
Stop pretending.

12
00:01:33,940 --> 00:01:35,570
Do you even know where you are?

13
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:37,460
I could kill you in a second, you know.

14
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:38,530
Not to be rude, but you sure talk a lot.

15
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:39,140
Why so many words?

16
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:40,780
I told you, I'm just here to make money.

17
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:41,570
But you don't believe me anyway.

18
00:01:41,570 --> 00:01:42,740
If you've got the guts, kill me. Go ahead.

19
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:44,610
Tell me who you really are.

20
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:45,500
I'm your father.

21
00:01:48,970 --> 00:01:50,020
Within three steps,

22
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:53,060
you could've shot Xiao Le right away.

23
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,610
But you deliberately backed down.

24
00:01:55,820 --> 00:01:57,210
Then you disarmed him with your bare hands.

25
00:01:57,210 --> 00:01:58,740
And you purposely spilled water at the workstation.

26
00:01:58,740 --> 00:02:00,210
Do you think I'm blind?

27
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,250
So what?

28
00:02:05,570 --> 00:02:06,780
Did I forget to tell you?

29
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:08,970
I've already found out your real identity.

30
00:02:10,930 --> 00:02:11,820
But

31
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:17,420
I want to hear you say it yourself.

32
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,210
If you've already found out who I am,

33
00:02:21,370 --> 00:02:23,210
then you should know the consequences of killing me.

34
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:24,370
Kid,

35
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:27,010
you're getting a bit cocky.

36
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:30,340
You're even more arrogant than I am.

37
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:32,060
The police back home already know what's going on here.

38
00:02:32,060 --> 00:02:33,500
It's only a matter of time before they track us down here.

39
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:36,210
Are you trying to drag us all down with you?

40
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,650
Do you think that when the police from home arrive,

41
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,810
you'll be able to get away?

42
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:43,500
Feng Zhou.

43
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:46,290
Qin Lang.

44
00:02:47,090 --> 00:02:47,900
Qin Lang.

45
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:51,290
Gao Man, have you seen Qin Lang?

46
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,420
I want him to play Feng Zhou.

47
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:54,420
Senior, don't worry.

48
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:55,370
I'll go look for him.

49
00:02:55,810 --> 00:02:56,010
Okay.

50
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,210
Please give him this script for me.

51
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:57,810
Okay.

52
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:58,570
Alright, don't worry.

53
00:02:59,290 --> 00:03:00,420
You'll go straight on stage in a bit.

54
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:01,090
Wait a minute.

55
00:03:02,290 --> 00:03:03,420
Why do you all get to play the police

56
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:04,140
while I have to play the drug dealer?

57
00:03:04,370 --> 00:03:04,620
I'm not doing it.

58
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,290
Aren't you the one who knows this drug dealer best?

59
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:08,500
Why can't you play him?

60
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,850
I know Feng Zhou because I want to catch him,

61
00:03:09,850 --> 00:03:10,810
not because I want to play him.

62
00:03:11,140 --> 00:03:12,370
How about I treat you to a meal?

63
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,540
This isn't about food.

64
00:03:13,650 --> 00:03:14,500
This is a matter of principle.

65
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:15,210
You're really not going to do it?

66
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:15,900
I'm really not.

67
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:16,780
Alright then.

68
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:18,930
I even told Senior

69
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:20,210
that I could definitely convince you.

70
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,250
So we could finish the performance.

71
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:24,300
Looks like I overestimated myself.

72
00:03:24,780 --> 00:03:25,780
I'll try to think of another way.

73
00:03:29,460 --> 00:03:30,020
Wait.

74
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:34,650
Fine, I'll help you this one time.

75
00:03:42,090 --> 00:03:43,210
